<br>
So people are using the strategy to cast a new pet every fight, reclaiming it for more mana than they used to summon it AFTER fight when it killed the mob. Some peeps are also using it with chaining, but in my opinion that is a bit risky and doesnt help speed up the fight.<br>
<br>
So what you do is, summon pet, BO and DS it, let it fight, then reclaim and voila you end up with more mana then before (if you are using pants and robe for DS and BO).<br>
<br>
Hope that helps ... greets ... Mel<br>
<br>
